Hey Fam! Allow me to reintroduce myself.

My name is MaryJane. I’ve been working the front desk at No Egrets for about 2 years now! So if you’ve stopped by the studio, you’ve probably seen this friendly face greeting you at the door.☺️

While working the desk I found a love and passion for piercings. So I decided to take a leap of faith and I am now a full time piercing apprentice! 🥳 I’ve been apprenticing for 5 months now and it has been such a lovely and challenging experience. I’ve done at least a dozen change outs. 

In a few weeks I’ll be posting for some practice piercings so be on the lookout! And always feel free to just stop by and say hi!😁💗
